title: The Log-Cabin Lady
creator: Annonymous
description:
LibriVox recording of The Log-Cabin Lady, by Unknown. 'The story of The Log-Cabin Lady is one of the annals of America. It is a moving record of the conquest of self-consciousness and fear through mastery of manners and customs. It has been written by one who has not sacrificed the strength and honesty of her pioneer girlhood, but who added to these qualities that graciousness and charm which have given her distinction on two continents.'
(frome the introduction) M4B format available For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
